name: Forging
title: 锻造
desc:
The obtained gear blueprints can be crafted into weapons through the forging system. 
In addition, crafting a gear requires both coins and weeks. 
By upgrading the town's facilities, the forging system can be strengthened.

name: Recruit
title: 招募
desc:
Spend your funds here to recruit new characters. 
The funds for recruitment will increase each time. 
New characters will become available for recruitment every few weeks. 
By upgrading the town's facilities, the recruitment system can be strengthened.

name: Rest
title: 疗养
desc:
Put characters in Spots to accelerate their recovery. 
By upgrading the town's facilities, the rest system can be enhanced.

name: Training
title: 训练
desc: Select a character and spend coins and weeks to train him. Training types: exp training, skill training, and tailored training. Exp Training: the character can gain plenty of exp. Skill Training: the character can learn a new skill. Special training: a character who is eligible can receive innate effects after completing the training.

name: Memory Crystal
title: 网游角色碎片回收
condition: Unlockable after obtaining extra character shards

name: Gear Engraving
title: 网游武器附魔
condition: Unlocked after clearing The Fool's Journey 8-5

name: Tower of Adversity
title: 深渊
condition: Unlocks after clearing the 5th floor of Tower of Conquest

name: Voyage Momento
title: 生涯纪念册
condition: Clear The Fool's Journey 1-2 to unlock
